      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • city
          ConcurrentHashMap<String,List<String>> city
          A thread-safe map that holds the current state of the grid. Keys are positions in the grid, and values are lists of vehicle information at those positions.
        • matrixPanel
          MatrixPanel matrixPanel
          The panel that renders the matrix/grid.
        • previousPosition
          Map<String,String> previousPosition
          A map that keeps track of the previous positions of vehicles. The key is the vehicle information, and the value is the previous position.
